<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Register</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/output.css" />
  </head>
  <body class="w-full h-screen bg-white flex text-black ">
    <div id="loader" class="loader-overlay hidden">
      <div class="loader"></div>
    </div>
    <% if(error.length>0){%>
      <div class="absolute top-5 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 p-3 rounded-md bg-red-500 z-10">
        <span class="inline-block mt-1 mb-1 text-white">
          <%=error%>
        </span>
      </div>
    <%} %>
    <% if(success.length>0){%>
      <div class="absolute top-5 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 p-3 rounded-md bg-green-500 z-10">
        <span class="inline-block mt-1 mb-1 text-white">
          <%=success%>
        </span>
      </div>
    <%} %>
    <div class="relative w-1/2 h-full animate-fade-in">
      <img
        class="w-full h-full object-center transition-transform duration-700 hover:scale-105"
        src="/images/register-login.webp"
        alt=""
      />
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/70 rounded-lg flex-col flex justify-end p-5 items-center gap-6 text-white"
      >
        <p class="text-3xl font-bold animate-fade-in-up">Time is Money</p>
        <p class="text-center text-md animate-fade-in-up delay-100">
          Time isn't just measured in seconds—it's measured in value. Every tick
          of the second hand represents opportunity, productivity, and legacy. A
          luxury watch doesn't just tell time; it embodies the discipline to
          seize every moment.
        </p>
        <div
          class="w-full h-px bg-linear-to-r from-gray-700 via-white/30 to-gray-700"
        ></div>
        <p class="text-center text-md font-semibold animate-fade-in-up delay-200">
          "A man with a watch knows what time it is. A man with two watches is
          never sure."
        </p>
        <p class="self-end mr-30 italic animate-fade-in-up delay-300">~ Anonymous</p>
        <div
          class="w-full h-px bg-linear-to-r from-gray-700 via-white/30 to-gray-700"
        ></div>
        <p class="text-center text-md animate-fade-in-up delay-400">
          Wear your watch. Own your time. Build your empire.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-1/2 h-full flex justify-center items-center flex-col gap-10 animate-fade-in-up">
      <a href="javascript:history.back()" class="self-start ml-12 hover:translate-x-[-5px] transition-transform">Back</a>
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">Sign In</h1>
      <form
        class="w-1/2 flex flex-col items-start justify-center gap-10"
        action="/login"
        method="post"
      >
        <label
          for="name"
          class="w-full flex gap-2 justify-center items-start flex-col"
        >
          <p class="text-xl font-bold">Name:</p>
          <input
            class="p-4 bg-slate-300 outline-none rounded-xl w-full input-animate"
            type="text"
            name="name"
            required
          />
        </label>
        <label
          for="email"
          class="w-full flex gap-2 justify-center items-start flex-col"
        >
          <p class="text-xl font-bold">Email:</p>
          <input
            class="p-4 bg-slate-300 outline-none rounded-xl w-full input-animate"
            type="email"
            name="email"
            required
          />
        </label>
        <label
          for="password"
          class="w-full flex gap-2 justify-center items-start flex-col"
        >
          <p class="text-xl font-bold">Password:</p>
          <input
            class="p-4 bg-slate-300 outline-none rounded-xl w-full input-animate"
            type="password"
            name="password"
            required
          />
        </label>
        <button
          class="self-center text-xl font-bold bg-slate-300 py-4 px-8 rounded-2xl cursor-pointer btn-animate"
          type="submit"
        >
          Sign In
        </button>
      </form>
      <p class="tracking-widest text-md">
        Don't have an account?
        <a class="hover:border-b-2 transition-all" href="/register">Sign Up</a> instead
      </p>
    </div>
    <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
